
# game/story.rpy:1049
translate spanish story_db25eb83:

    # mc "Aaah, um...it's not really a date."
    mc "Ahhh... que va, no es una cita."

# game/story.rpy:1050
translate spanish story_314b9d80:

    # "I feel my own nervousness mixing with Meiji's, but I struggle for control."
    "Siento que mis propios nervios se mezclan con los de Meiji, pero lucho por mantener el control."

# game/story.rpy:1051
translate spanish story_b4499ac6:

    # mc "C-Come on, Sayori."
    mc "V-Vamos, Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:1053
translate spanish story_07888e2b:

    # s "Ehehe, alright Meiji."
    s "Je, je, je. Vale, Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:1059
translate spanish story_c0f42ce8:

    # "She puts on her shoes."
    "Se pone los zapatos."

# game/story.rpy:1060
translate spanish story_5a63362f:

    # sm "Have fun you twoooo-!"
    sm "¡Pasaoslo bien los dooos!"

# game/story.rpy:1061
translate spanish story_0c7af744:

    # "Sayori's mother chuckles and I can hear the amusement in her voice as the door shuts behind us."
    "La madre de Sayori suelta una risita y puedo escuchar lo mucho que se divierte mientras la puerta se cierra a nuestras espaldas."

# game/story.rpy:1068
translate spanish story_21de4c21:

    # s "Sorry about Mom."
    s "Siento lo de mi madre."

# game/story.rpy:1070
translate spanish story_c397e04a:

    # "Sayori looks a bit nervous and worried. I try and think what to say to put her at her ease."
    "Sayori parece un poco nerviosa y preocupada. Intento pensar en qué decirle para que se relaje."

# game/story.rpy:1071
translate spanish story_25561b98:

    # mc "Don't worry about it, I know how it is. My mom's similar. Now, let's just enjoy the day, shall we?"
    mc "No te preocupes, sé lo que se siente. Mi madre es igual. Ahora, hay que disfrutar del día, ¿vale?"

# game/story.rpy:1073
translate spanish story_d17e63d8:

    # s "Yeah! Where are we going first?"
    s "¡Sí! ¿Adónde vamos?"

# game/story.rpy:1075
translate spanish story_e106274a:

    # mc "Well, since I'm guessing you haven't had any breakfast yet, why don't we go get some food?"
    mc "Bueno, como supongo que aún no has desayunado nada, ¿por qué no vamos a comer algo?"

# game/story.rpy:1077
translate spanish story_2833216f:

    # s "Yes, please!"
    s "¡Sí, por favor!"

# game/story.rpy:1079
translate spanish story_6f73d325:

    # cm "{i}Off to that café then. Just follow my directions.{/i}"
    cm "{i}A esa cafetería entonces. Tú sigue mis indicaciones.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1080
translate spanish story_aa62be17:

    # mc "{b}Alright, but let's make this fun.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Ya, pero vamos a hacerlo divertido.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1081
translate spanish story_a434202d:

    # mc "Perfect. Now I want you to close your eyes."
    mc "Vale, quiero que cierres los ojos."

# game/story.rpy:1083
translate spanish story_f10f3702:

    # s "Eeeh? How come?"
    s "¿Ehhh? ¿Y eso?"

# game/story.rpy:1085
translate spanish story_10bf4b4f:

    # mc "I want it to be a surprise. Come on, I'll lead you."
    mc "Quiero que sea una sorpresa. Venga, yo te guío."

# game/story.rpy:1086
translate spanish story_122fef6f:

    # "Reaching over, I take her hand."
    "Extiendo el brazo y le cojo la mano."

# game/story.rpy:1088
translate spanish story_eef0aa19:

    # "Sayori's cheeks flush a bit the moment I take her hand."
    "Las mejillas de Sayori se sonrojan un poco en el momento en el que le cojo la mano."

# game/story.rpy:1090
translate spanish story_c351854e:

    # "She closes her eyes."
    "Ella cierra los ojos."

# game/story.rpy:1092
translate spanish story_d591512a:

    # s "I'm ready."
    s "Estoy lista."

# game/story.rpy:1094
translate spanish story_555a3386:

    # "I begin leading her down the street."
    "Empiezo a guiarla por la calle."

# game/story.rpy:1099
translate spanish story_48f4acd4:

    # "As we walk, Meiji begins imitating a standard computerized GPS voice."
    "A medida que caminamos, Meiji empieza a imitar la típica voz de un GPS."

# game/story.rpy:1100
translate spanish story_8d4e1181:

    # cm "{i}Keep going straight for two point four meters, then turn left.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Sigue recto durante dos coma cuatro metros, luego gira a la izquierda.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1101
translate spanish story_d5470225:

    # "At least he's making jokes. He's coping, which is more than I would be able to do in his situation."
    "Al menos hace bromas. Lo está sobrellevando, que es más de lo que yo podría hacer en su situación."

# game/story.rpy:1102
translate spanish story_2960bb30:

    # mc "{b}Cheeky bastard.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Serás capullo.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1103
translate spanish story_e57a4101:

    # "As we walk, I take in the scenery before me. The neighborhood is a bit higher up than the rest of the city, probably middle-class."
    "A medida que andamos, me fijo en el paisaje que tengo ante mí. El barrio está un poco más elevado que el resto de la ciudad, probablemente sea de clase media."

# game/story.rpy:1104
translate spanish story_ff27a3cc:

    # "The neighborhood itself appears to appeal to the better off, with most of the houses being two stories with an occasional three-story house."
    "El barrio en sí parece atraer a los más pudientes, ya que la mayoría de las casas son de dos plantas, con alguna ocasional de tres."

# game/story.rpy:1109
translate spanish story_9dabf5be:

    # "Meiji leads me down the streets towards an apparently older section of the suburb."
    "Meiji me guía por las calles hacia una parte que parece más antigua del barrio."

# game/story.rpy:1110
translate spanish story_3edea286:

    # "The buildings look a lot older than where Meiji's house is."
    "Los edificios parecen mucho más viejos que en la zona donde está la casa de Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:1111
translate spanish story_241e9328:

    # "I make sure I keep an eye on Sayori."
    "Me aseguro de no quitarle el ojo de encima a Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:1112
translate spanish story_378ac6bb:

    # "We keep walking until I spot a café."
    "Seguimos andando hasta que veo una cafetería."

# game/story.rpy:1117
translate spanish story_667cf20e:

    # "I stop in front of the entrance."
    "Me detengo frente a la entrada."

# game/story.rpy:1118
translate spanish story_81edd260:

    # mc "{b}Is this the place?{/b}"
    mc "{i}¿Es aquí?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1119
translate spanish story_0004ab20_1:

    # cm "{i}Yep.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Sí.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1120
translate spanish story_fac1d255:

    # mc "{b}Pretty old school. I like it.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Bastante clásico. Me gusta.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1122
translate spanish story_ef51cf83:

    # mc "We're here! You can open your eyes now."
    mc "¡Ya estamos! Ya puedes abrir los ojos."

# game/story.rpy:1124
translate spanish story_d0f65838:

    # "Sayori slowly opens her eyes."
    "Sayori abre los ojos poco a poco."

# game/story.rpy:1126
translate spanish story_a1b432ca:

    # s "Meiji...you remembered?!"
    s "Meiji... ¡¿Te acuerdas?!"

# game/story.rpy:1128
translate spanish story_3f6a3f80:

    # mc "I remember a lot of things. Come on, let's go inside."
    mc "Me acuerdo de muchas cosas. Venga, entremos."

# game/story.rpy:1136
translate spanish story_97b3f1a7:

    # "We head inside. I notice it's pretty old school inside as well."
    "Entramos. Me doy cuenta de que el interior también es bastante clásico."

# game/story.rpy:1138
translate spanish story_2c36015c:

    # mc "Now, let's get you something to eat."
    mc "Venga, vamos a pillarte algo de comer."

# game/story.rpy:1140
translate spanish story_d1906eb7:

    # s "Cinnamon buns!"
    s "¡Rollitos de canela!"

# game/story.rpy:1142
translate spanish story_566bac4a:

    # cm "{i}She loves the buns from here.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Le encantan los rollos de aquí.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1143
translate spanish story_0f3151ec:

    # mc "{b}That makes sense. Good call.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Cómo no. Bien elegido.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1144
translate spanish story_9ee72cbd:

    # mc "How many cinnamon buns do you want?"
    mc "¿Cuántos rollos de canela quieres?"

# game/story.rpy:1146
translate spanish story_97de62f7:

    # s "Three!"
    s "¡Tres!"

# game/story.rpy:1148
translate spanish story_ef714cba:

    # "I look over at the display and see that the buns are almost as big as her head and practically covered in glaze."
    "Echo un vistazo al mostrador y veo que los rollos son casi tan grandes como su cabeza y están prácticamente cubiertos de glaseado."

# game/story.rpy:1149
translate spanish story_84f91a5d:

    # mc "Really? Are you sure?"
    mc "¿En serio? ¿Estás segura?"

# game/story.rpy:1151
translate spanish story_0b0fa1a2:

    # s "Mmhmm!"
    s "Mmm... ¡Sí!"

# game/story.rpy:1152
translate spanish story_18e6f5d2:

    # mc "Anything to drink?"
    mc "¿Algo para beber?"

# game/story.rpy:1154
translate spanish story_229ea366:

    # s "Hot chocolate."
    s "Chocolate caliente."

# game/story.rpy:1156
translate spanish story_a61ace25:

    # cm "{i}Same old Sayori.{/i}"
    cm "{i}La Sayori de siempre.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1157
translate spanish story_4ae70b05:

    # mc "Same old Sayori."
    mc "La Sayori de siempre."

# game/story.rpy:1158
translate spanish story_462c3ff7:

    # "I ruffle her hair a bit."
    "Le revuelvo un poco el pelo."

# game/story.rpy:1160
translate spanish story_18d8c283:

    # s "Hey! Meanie..."
    s "¡Oye! Malo..."

# game/story.rpy:1161
translate spanish story_c3e73b28:

    # "Sayori pouts at me. I hold up my hands in surrender."
    "Sayori me hace un puchero. Levanto las manos en señal de rendición."

# game/story.rpy:1162
translate spanish story_d963dc70:

    # mc "Alright, alright, sorry."
    mc "Vale, vale, lo siento."

# game/story.rpy:1164
translate spanish story_7c4d07cd:

    # s "I'll only forgive you if you get me four buns."
    s "Solo te perdonaré si me compras cuatro rollos."

# game/story.rpy:1166
translate spanish story_5cfd0a9a:

    # mc "Four?! Sayori, are you sure you can eat that much?"
    mc "¡¿Cuatro?! Sayori, ¿estás segura de que puedes comer tanto?"

# game/story.rpy:1168
translate spanish story_34b61c7e:

    # s "Yep!"
    s "¡Sí!"

# game/story.rpy:1170
translate spanish story_482ea448:

    # "I sigh. Looking at the line of customers I see that there are a few ahead of me."
    "Lanzo un suspiro. Al mirar la cola de clientes, veo que hay unos cuantos por delante de mí."

# game/story.rpy:1171
translate spanish story_8502f53d:

    # mc "Fine, four buns. Why don't you go find us a place to sit while I get the food? No point in the both of us standing in line."
    mc "Está bien, cuatro rollos. ¿Por qué no vas a buscarnos un sitio para sentarnos mientras pido? No tiene sentido que los dos hagamos cola."

# game/story.rpy:1173
translate spanish story_4808ca3e:

    # s "Alright."
    s "Vale."

# game/story.rpy:1176
translate spanish story_273be155:

    # "Sayori dashes off to a corner seat. I get in line and wait to order."
    "Sayori se va corriendo hacia un asiento en una esquina. Yo me pongo a esperar."

# game/story.rpy:1177
translate spanish story_2b3c685a:

    # mc "{b}Hey, do you drink coffee?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Oye, ¿tú bebes café?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1178
translate spanish story_03e295d2:

    # cm "{i}I do. Black please.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Sí. Solo, por favor.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1179
translate spanish story_0db16936:

    # "Damn, I hate coffee, but perhaps Meiji's tastebuds are different than mine."
    "Joder, odio el café, pero quizás los gustos de Meiji sean distintas a los míos."

# game/story.rpy:1180
translate spanish story_ddc42fec:

    # "I wait in line until it's my turn. I approach the counter where I'm greeted by a smiling cashier about my age."
    "Espero en la cola hasta que llega mi turno. Me acerco al mostrador donde me recibe una cajera sonriente de mi edad."

# game/story.rpy:1182
translate spanish story_a7e92439:

    # c "Hello sir, and welcome to Café Forté. What can I get for you today?"
    c "Hola, señor, bienvenido al Café Forté. ¿Qué le pongo hoy?"

# game/story.rpy:1184
translate spanish story_0365aeb8:

    # "Hmm...the name on her badge says Kotonoha."
    "Mmm... el nombre en su placa dice Kotonoha."

# game/story.rpy:1185
translate spanish story_c676a4ce:

    # mc "Can I have four of your cinnamon buns, a tall hot chocolate, the sausage breakfast bagel and a medium black coffee, please?"
    mc "¿Me pone cuatro rollos de canela, un chocolate caliente grande, el bagel de desayuno con salchicha y un café solo mediano, por favor?"

# game/story.rpy:1186
translate spanish story_aea40af2:

    # cm "{i}Make that a large, please.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Que sea grande, por favor.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1187
translate spanish story_4e837b5b:

    # mc "{b}Your digestive system is going to hate us in the morning.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Tu cuerpo nos va a odiar por la mañana.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1188
translate spanish story_689754ad:

    # mc "Sorry, make that a large coffee."
    mc "Perdón, que el café sea grande."

# game/story.rpy:1189
translate spanish story_ad9eeafd:

    # ko 3wd "Of course! Is there anything else?"
    ko 3wd "¡Por supuesto! ¿Alguna cosa más?"

# game/story.rpy:1191
translate spanish story_bffe481b:

    # mc "Nope, that should do it, thank you."
    mc "No, eso es todo, gracias."

# game/story.rpy:1192
translate spanish story_5e49515e:

    # ko 1wd "Would you like us to heat up the cinnamon buns?"
    ko 1wd "¿Le gustaría que calentáramos los rollos de canela?"

# game/story.rpy:1194
translate spanish story_ead51c30:

    # cm "{i}Sayori used to love getting them heated up, if I remember right.{/i}"
    cm "{i}A Sayori le encantaba que se los calentaran, si no recuerdo mal.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1195
translate spanish story_afdffd0d:

    # mc "Yes, please."
    mc "Sí, por favor."

# game/story.rpy:1196
translate spanish story_72a33d21:

    # ko 3wl "Thank you sir, that will be ¥3094."
    ko 3wl "Gracias, señor, serán 3,094 yenes."

# game/story.rpy:1198
translate spanish story_80151d74:

    # "Her cheerful behavior is infectious and I return her customer service smile with a small one of my own."
    "Su comportamiento alegre es contagioso y le devuelvo su sonrisa de servicio al cliente con una pequeña sonrisa."

# game/story.rpy:1201
translate spanish story_d7496329:

    # "I pay for the food, step to the side and wait for my order to be processed. The people ahead of me grab their orders and rush out."
    "Pago la comida, me hago a un lado y espero a que procesen mi pedido. Las personas delante de mí agarran sus pedidos y se van a toda prisa."

# game/story.rpy:1202
translate spanish story_6f040089:

    # mc "{b}Oh yeah, tell me a bit about your sister. What's her major?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Ah, sí, cuéntame un poco sobre tu hermana. ¿Qué estudia?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1203
translate spanish story_9ea9f094:

    # cm "{i}She's a lot more of a free spirit than I am. Her major in school is Linguistic Communications or something like that with a minor in Library Science.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Es un espíritu mucho más libre que yo. Estudia Comunicación Lingüística o algo así, con una especialización en Biblioteconomía.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1204
translate spanish story_6b795760:

    # "I never knew that was an actual degree. Interesting. That sounds like a degree that might interest Yuri."
    "No sabía que eso fuera una carrera real. Interesante. Suena como algo que podría interesarle a Yuri."

# game/story.rpy:1205
translate spanish story_454ef867:

    # cm "{i}She was the President of the Literature Club when she was in high school before it disbanded, after all.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Después de todo, fue la presidenta del club de literatura cuando estaba en el instituto, antes de que se disolviera.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1206
translate spanish story_25d651a0:

    # mc "{b}Wait, she was in the Literature Club? Why was it disbanded?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Espera, ¿estaba en el club de literatura? ¿Por qué se disolvió?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1207
translate spanish story_4f84df2d:

    # cm "{i}All the members graduated.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Todos los miembros se graduaron.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1208
translate spanish story_68ec1191:

    # "I sigh in relief."
    "Suspiro de alivio."

# game/story.rpy:1209
translate spanish story_8564dbee:

    # mc "{b}Makes sense.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Tiene sentido para mí.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1211
translate spanish story_a4717c5f:

    # ko "Sir? Here's your order."
    ko "¿Señor? Aquí tiene su pedido."

# game/story.rpy:1213
translate spanish story_991c04e9:

    # "I turn and see the cashier looking at me expectantly. On the counter is a tray with two coffee mugs, one with my coffee and the other with the hot chocolate."
    "Me giro y veo a la cajera mirándome expectante. En el mostrador hay una bandeja con dos tazas, una con mi café y la otra con el chocolate caliente."

# game/story.rpy:1214
translate spanish story_d088383e:

    # "Next to them are the breakfast bagel and cinnamon buns wrapped up neatly."
    "Al lado están el bagel de desayuno y los rollos de canela cuidadosamente envueltos."

# game/story.rpy:1215
translate spanish story_02f39719:

    # mc "Ah, right, thank you."
    mc "Ah, vale, gracias."

# game/story.rpy:1216
translate spanish story_93c72496:

    # "I take the tray."
    "Tomo la bandeja."

# game/story.rpy:1217
translate spanish story_57b1c1ea:

    # ko 1wd "You're welcome, and enjoy!"
    ko 1wd "¡De nada, que lo disfrute!"

# game/story.rpy:1218
translate spanish story_215fc4cc:

    # ko 7wl "Our pastries are second to none, after all."
    ko 7wl "Al fin y al cabo, nuestra repostería es insuperable."

# game/story.rpy:1219
translate spanish story_ff0e835a:

    # "Huh, interesting girl."
    "Mmm, menuda chica."

# game/story.rpy:1222
translate spanish story_0f6ed940:

    # "She turns back to her register to help the next customer. I walk back to Sayori."
    "Se vuelve a su caja registradora para atender al siguiente cliente. Vuelvo con Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:1228
translate spanish story_39751967:

    # cm "{i}I...guess she really does have depression...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Supongo... que de verdad tiene depresión...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1229
translate spanish story_054183d1:

    # mc "{b}Don't worry, we can help her manage that.{/b}"
    mc "{i}No te preocupes, podemos ayudarla a lidiar con eso.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1230
translate spanish story_bc4571e9:

    # "I set the tray down loudly."
    "Dejo la bandeja haciendo ruido."

# game/story.rpy:1232
translate spanish story_8eb1b99b:

    # mc "Wakey wakey, Sayori! All our food is here and ready."
    mc "¡Sayori, levanta! Toda la comida está aquí y lista."

# game/story.rpy:1233
translate spanish story_7a367a9a:

    # "What do you know? I rhymed!"
    "¡Anda! ¡He hecho una rima!"

# game/story.rpy:1235
translate spanish story_605c16b8:

    # s "Ah, sorry Meiji. I was spacing out."
    s "Ah, lo siento Meiji. Estaba un tanto distraída."

# game/story.rpy:1236
translate spanish story_846194c6:

    # "I reach over and flick her forehead a bit."
    "Me acerco y le doy un golpecito en la frente."

# game/story.rpy:1237
translate spanish story_e1a8dcc3:

    # mc "Try not to do that so much."
    mc "Intenta no hacerlo tanto."

# game/story.rpy:1239
translate spanish story_8d90eadc:

    # s "Ow! Meanie!"
    s "¡Ey! ¡Malo!"

# game/story.rpy:1241
translate spanish story_65daf1a8:

    # mc "Well, this meanie just paid for four of those cinnamon buns you like so much."
    mc "Bueno, este malo acaba de pagar cuatro de esos rollos de canela que tanto te gustan."

# game/story.rpy:1243
translate spanish story_5842b2ec:

    # "Sayori begins drooling."
    "Sayori empieza a babear."

# game/story.rpy:1245
translate spanish story_bb0dae95:

    # s "Itadakimasu!"
    s "¡Itadakimasu!"

# game/story.rpy:1247
translate spanish story_30cd4e3b:

    # "Sayori grabs the first bun and takes a massive bite out of it. I chuckle, rip off a small portion of another one and take a bite."
    "Sayori agarra el primer rollo y le da un mordisco enorme. Me río, arranco un trocito de otro y le doy un bocado."

# game/story.rpy:1249
translate spanish story_6ad3a710:

    # s "Shoo good~!"
    s "Qué riiico..."

# game/story.rpy:1251
translate spanish story_4b181d3c:

    # "I take a bite."
    "Le doy un mordisco."

# game/story.rpy:1252
translate spanish story_a7176c6d:

    # "No kidding...this is really good!"
    "Que no es broma... ¡está buenísimo!"

# game/story.rpy:1253
translate spanish story_ce395973:

    # "The buns are, to my surprise, somewhat crisp on the outside, with a heavenly soft and warm center. The glaze only enhances the experience of the little bit of bun I have."
    "Para mi sorpresa, los rollos están un poco crujientes por fuera, con un centro divinamente suave y caliente. El glaseado solo mejora la experiencia del trocito de rollo que tengo."

# game/story.rpy:1254
translate spanish story_7cdb77bc:

    # mc "Man, these are good. I regret not getting one for me. Although knowing you, you'd just steal it from me."
    mc "Vaya, están muy buenos. Me arrepiento de no haber pedido uno para mí. Aunque conociéndote, seguro que me lo robarías."

# game/story.rpy:1255
translate spanish story_69f68f6c:

    # cm "{i}You know, you're doing a good job of imitating how I'd tease her at least.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Sabes, al menos estás haciendo un buen trabajo imitando cómo me burlaría de ella.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1256
translate spanish story_db470077:

    # mc "{b}I try.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Lo intento.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1258
translate spanish story_c8f9f724:

    # "Sayori suddenly looks nervous."
    "De repente, Sayori parece nerviosa."

# game/story.rpy:1259
translate spanish story_8c69e160:

    # s "If you want, I can split one with you."
    s "Si quieres, puedo compartir uno contigo."

# game/story.rpy:1260
translate spanish story_501e40b6:

    # mc "No, I don't want to deprive you of the experience of devouring such delicious goodies. I've got my own food here, so don't worry about me."
    mc "No, no quiero privarte de la experiencia de devorar unas delicias tan ricas. Tengo mi propia comida aquí, así que no te preocupes por mí."

# game/story.rpy:1261
translate spanish story_7a932080:

    # "I hold up my breakfast bagel."
    "Levanto mi bagel de desayuno."

# game/story.rpy:1263
translate spanish story_14f4ab55:

    # s "Alright..."
    s "Vale..."

# game/story.rpy:1264
translate spanish story_48fb23ba:

    # "She sounds a bit uncertain, but only for a moment before returning to her food."
    "Suena un poco insegura, pero solo por un momento antes de volver a su comida."

# game/story.rpy:1267
translate spanish story_566048c1:

    # "I take a bite of my food. The bagel is plain. Inside there's a square of scrambled eggs, cheddar cheese and a round sausage patty."
    "Doy un bocado a mi comida. El bagel es normal. Dentro hay un trozo de huevos revueltos, queso cheddar y una salchicha."

# game/story.rpy:1268
translate spanish story_cf504dd6:

    # "The breakfast bagel is just as savory and full of umami as the bun was sweet and fluffy."
    "El bagel de desayuno es tan sabroso y lleno de umami como el rollo era dulce y esponjoso."

# game/story.rpy:1269
translate spanish story_de990574:

    # mc "{b}The food in this world is a lot better than mine.{/b}"
    mc "{i}La comida de este mundo es mucho mejor que la del mío.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1270
translate spanish story_e2f5d05e:

    # cm "{i}Or maybe we Japanese have a better handle on food than you fat Americans.{/i}"
    cm "{i}O tal vez los japoneses tenemos mejor mano para la comida que vosotros, los estadounidenses gordos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1271
translate spanish story_0ed22193:

    # "His tone is teasing now."
    "Su tono ahora es burlón."

# game/story.rpy:1272
translate spanish story_98a497c5:

    # mc "{b}Oy! Not fair! I am not fat!{/b}"
    mc "{i}¡Oye, no estoy gordo!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1273
translate spanish story_a9217189:

    # cm "{i}Who says Sayori is the only one I get to tease?{/i}"
    cm "{i}¿Quién dice que Sayori es la única a la que puedo molestar?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1274
translate spanish story_55a4f5b7:

    # mc "{b}You sneaky little devil.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Puto chaval astuto.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1275
translate spanish story_cbe5b19b:

    # "I take a sip of the coffee. I'm not a coffee fan, but with these new taste buds I see why Meiji likes it black."
    "Doy un sorbo al café. No soy muy fan del café, pero con estas nuevas papilas gustativas, veo por qué a Meiji le gusta solo."

# game/story.rpy:1276
translate spanish story_dd109832:

    # "It's got a bitter taste, but in an enjoyable way."
    "Tiene un sabor amargo, pero agradable."

# game/story.rpy:1277
translate spanish story_ef6fecf4:

    # "I continue to eat and wash the bagel down with sips of coffee."
    "Sigo comiendo y acompaño el bagel con pequeños sorbos de café."

# game/story.rpy:1279
translate spanish story_de36bd17:

    # "Sayori is already on her second bun, her face all messy and sticky."
    "Sayori ya va por su segundo bollo y tiene la cara pringosa y pegajosa."

# game/story.rpy:1280
translate spanish story_9105a86f:

    # "I chuckle and hand her one of the damp towels the restaurant gave us."
    "Me río y le tiendo una de las toallitas húmedas que nos dio el restaurante."

# game/story.rpy:1282
translate spanish story_31cc3058:

    # mc "You should wipe your face."
    mc "Deberías limpiarte la cara."

# game/story.rpy:1284
translate spanish story_8f81103d:

    # "Taking the towel from me, she wipes her mouth clean then resumes eating."
    "Me quita la toallita, se limpia la boca y sigue comiendo."

# game/story.rpy:1285
translate spanish story_658f1ad5:

    # "However just as quickly she gets her face messy again."
    "Aunque tarda muy poco en volver a pringarse la cara."

# game/story.rpy:1287
translate spanish story_189bca65:

    # "I decide to ignore it until she's finished."
    "Decido no darle importancia hasta que termine."

# game/story.rpy:1288
translate spanish story_41bc63e8:

    # mc "{b}What would you do in a situation like this?{/b}"
    mc "{i}¿Qué harías en una situación así?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1289
translate spanish story_3a3b3b29:

    # cm "{i}Ask her how she's been. The last time we really ever talked was a few months ago when she was first talking about forming her club. Or ask about her club.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Preguntarle qué tal le va. La última vez que de verdad hablamos fue hace un par de meses, cuando empezó a decir que quería crear un club. O preguntarle por el club.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1290
translate spanish story_ed77c04c:

    # "I take another bite of breakfast bagel then wash it down with the coffee."
    "Le doy otro bocado al bagel y me lo paso con un trago de café."

# game/story.rpy:1291
translate spanish story_bcc6feee:

    # mc "Hey, how's your club been? It's been a while since we've spent time together like this and we hardly ever get to see each other at school."
    mc "Oye, ¿qué tal te va con el club? Hacía mucho que no pasábamos el rato juntos de esta manera y en el insti apenas nos vemos."

# game/story.rpy:1293
translate spanish story_10b6a21f:

    # s "It's going great! We started a month ago after our President quit her last club."
    s "¡Nos va genial! Empezamos hace un mes, después de que nuestra presidenta dejase su anterior club."

# game/story.rpy:1295
translate spanish story_73c42e97:

    # s "Our club President is a really good leader, and the other members are pretty cool in their own way."
    s "La presidenta del club es una líder estupenda y las demás compis son muy guais, cada una a su manera."

# game/story.rpy:1297
translate spanish story_0b150b37:

    # mc "You're Vice President of the Literature Club, right?"
    mc "Eres la vicepresidenta del club de literatura, ¿no?"

# game/story.rpy:1299
translate spanish story_34b61c7e_1:

    # s "Yep!"
    s "¡Sí!"

# game/story.rpy:1300
translate spanish story_6a5c957b:

    # mc "So, what do you guys do in the club? Do you sit in a circle and read books aloud? Do you discuss your favorite books and the merits of each?"
    mc "Ya, ¿qué hacéis en el club? ¿Os sentáis en círculo a leer libros en voz alta? ¿Habláis sobre vuestros libros favoritos y las virtudes de cada uno?"

# game/story.rpy:1302
translate spanish story_82e30887:

    # s "We mostly just do our own thing."
    s "La mayoría de las veces cada una va a lo suyo."

# game/story.rpy:1304
translate spanish story_362f3d94:

    # s "Natsuki reads her manga, Yuri reads bigger books, and Monika spends a lot of her time trying to come up with activities for us to do together but she also writes sometimes too."
    s "Natsuki lee su manga, Yuri lee libros más grandes, y Monika se pasa casi todo el tiempo intentando organizar actividades para hacer todas juntas, aunque a veces también escribe."

# game/story.rpy:1305
translate spanish story_a1ef7c67:

    # s "Last week we read a book Yuri recommended called {i}Sense and Sensibility.{/i} That was fun, although Natsuki didn't really think so."
    s "La semana pasada leímos un libro que nos recomendó Yuri que se llama {i}Sensatez y sentimiento{/i}. Fue muy divertido, aunque Natsuki no pensaba lo mismo."

# game/story.rpy:1307
translate spanish story_23ef9b52:

    # mc "Wait, did you mention Monika?"
    mc "Espera, ¿has dicho Monika?"

# game/story.rpy:1309
translate spanish story_06a55388:

    # s "Huh? Oh yeah, I did. Do you know her?"
    s "¿Eh? Ah, sí. ¿La conoces?"

# game/story.rpy:1310
translate spanish story_e45aa17e:

    # mc "Does she have long hair, a white bow and green eyes? Because if so, I do know her. She and I were in the same class last year."
    mc "¿Tiene el pelo largo, un lazo blanco y los ojos verdes? Porque si es así, claro que la conozco. Íbamos juntos a clase el año pasado."

# game/story.rpy:1311
translate spanish story_830ce533:

    # mc "We didn't actually talk much."
    mc "Aunque no hablamos mucho."

# game/story.rpy:1313
translate spanish story_95909200:

    # s "Uwaah! Really?!"
    s "¡Hala! ¿De verdad?"

# game/story.rpy:1314
translate spanish story_7fdce05f:

    # "I chuckle at Sayori's cute reaction. I also feel my heartbeat increase."
    "Me río ante la simpática reacción de Sayori. Además, siento cómo mi corazón se acelera."

# game/story.rpy:1315
translate spanish story_7c0d0ccf:

    # cm "{i}Huh, guess I really do have a crush on her...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Vaya, parece que en el fondo sí que me gusta...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1316
translate spanish story_f99a2faf:

    # mc "{b}Good to hear. Let's turn the charm up to a ten.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Me alegra oírlo. Vamos a sacar a relucir todo nuestro encanto.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1317
translate spanish story_44de4b08:

    # "It had been a little while since I'd read that Jane Austen book, but I decide to ask anyway."
    "Hacía tiempo que no leía aquel libro de Jane Austen, pero decido preguntar de todas formas."

# game/story.rpy:1318
translate spanish story_f0214bfd:

    # mc "So, what did you think of the book you guys read last week?"
    mc "Y bien, ¿qué te pareció el libro que leísteis la semana pasada?"

# game/story.rpy:1320
translate spanish story_25704cf4:

    # s "Willoughby's a meanie! The way he leaves Marianne is just stupid! All for money? That's dumb!"
    s "¡Willoughby es un malo! ¡Dejar así a Marianne es de estúpidos! ¿Todo por dinero? ¡Es una tontería!"

# game/story.rpy:1322
translate spanish story_18f81008:

    # "Right! The story's coming back to me now."
    "¡Cierto! Ahora me acuerdo de la historia."

# game/story.rpy:1323
translate spanish story_c6e77e51:

    # mc "Don't you remember when Willoughby came by to see Marianne when she was sick near the end of the book? Remember that talk he had with Elinor?"
    mc "¿No te acuerdas de cuando Willoughby fue a ver a Marianne cuando estaba enferma, casi al final del libro? ¿Recuerdas aquella charla que tuvo con Elinor?"

# game/story.rpy:1325
translate spanish story_54bf3c9e:

    # s "Yeah, but he didn't have to be so mean!"
    s "Sí, ¡pero no tendría que haber sido tan malo!"

# game/story.rpy:1327
translate spanish story_64bd6910:

    # mc "Yeah that's fair. Who's your favorite character?"
    mc "Sí, es justo. ¿Quién es tu personaje favorito?"

# game/story.rpy:1329
translate spanish story_8baeefa2:

    # s "Marianne. I was happy when she ended up with the Colonel."
    s "Marianne. Me alegré un montón cuando acabó con el coronel."

# game/story.rpy:1331
translate spanish story_7f0123ce:

    # mc "Mine's actually Edward. I admire his loyalty and his refusal to bow to the pressure he was put on when his engagement to Lucy came to light."
    mc "Pues el mío es Edward. Admiro su lealtad y que se negase a ceder a la presión a la que le sometieron cuando salió a la luz su compromiso con Lucy."

# game/story.rpy:1333
translate spanish story_17d8d09c:

    # "Realization comes into Sayori's eyes."
    "Sayori se da cuenta de un detalle y abre mucho los ojos."

# game/story.rpy:1335
translate spanish story_47982d2e:

    # s "Wait...{b}{i}you read Sense and Sensibility{/b}{/i}!?"
    s "Un momento... ¡¿{b}{i}te has leído Sensatez y sentimiento{/i}{/b}?!"

# game/story.rpy:1336
translate spanish story_d2b16e26:

    # "She says that so loudly that other patrons look our way."
    "Lo dice tan alto que el resto de los clientes nos mira."

# game/story.rpy:1337
translate spanish story_7294a246:

    # mc "Whoa, calm down there."
    mc "Eh, calmada."

# game/story.rpy:1339
translate spanish story_d765853e:

    # s "But I thought you only read manga."
    s "Pero pensaba que solo leías manga."

# game/story.rpy:1341
translate spanish story_03816bce:

    # cm "{i}If I remember right, Mom has a copy of that book somewhere in the house. And a movie version.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Si no me equivoco, mamá tiene una copia de ese libro por algún lado de la casa. Y también una película.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1342
translate spanish story_4f568f98:

    # mc "I saw the book on the kitchen table a couple weeks ago. Mom likes those types of books and I guess curiosity got the better of me."
    mc "Vi el libro en la mesa de la cocina hace un par de semanas. A mamá le gustan este tipo de libros y, bueno, la curiosidad mató al gato."

# game/story.rpy:1343
translate spanish story_d045eb1d:

    # mc "It's not something I'd normally read, but I actually did enjoy it. Speaking of, I should look to see if there's a manga version."
    mc "No es algo que leería normalmente, pero la verdad es que me gustó. Hablando de eso, debería mirar si hay versión en manga."

# game/story.rpy:1345
translate spanish story_1fdbc72a:

    # s "That's the Meiji I know."
    s "Ese es el Meiji que conozco."

# game/story.rpy:1346
translate spanish story_ab8c00be:

    # cm "{i}Good save. I'd have never read such a story myself.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Buena salvada. En mi vida habría leído una historia así.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1347
translate spanish story_c17624dd:

    # mc "{b}It was part of a college class a couple terms ago. You should really give it a read sometime.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Fue parte de una asignatura de la universidad hace unos semestres. Deberías leerlo en algún momento.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1348
translate spanish story_a2cf1022:

    # mc "So, what else have you guys been doing?"
    mc "Y bueno, ¿qué más habéis estado haciendo?"

# game/story.rpy:1350
translate spanish story_251e1fd5:

    # s "We tried reading some short stories, but that didn't quite work out as Monika hoped."
    s "Intentamos leer algunas historias cortas, pero no salió tan bien como Monika esperaba."

# game/story.rpy:1352
translate spanish story_f7f8ef5b:

    # s "Natsuki wasn't much of a fan of the ones Yuri picked and Yuri didn't like the manga Natsuki hoped to read."
    s "A Natsuki no le gustaron las que escogió Yuri, y a Yuri no le gustó el manga que Natsuki quería leer."

# game/story.rpy:1354
translate spanish story_913f0640:

    # mc "Good to know someone in that club has the sense to realize that manga is literature."
    mc "Me alegra saber que alguien en el club tiene el raciocinio para darse cuenta de que el manga es literatura."

# game/story.rpy:1355
translate spanish story_50e621d7:

    # cm "{i}Damn right!{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Y que lo digas!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1357
translate spanish story_53f414fb:

    # s "Ehehe, you'd like her."
    s "Je, je, je. Os llevaríais bien."

# game/story.rpy:1358
translate spanish story_6ac68896:

    # "Her tone is strained, like she's forcing her smile."
    "Su tono de voz suena tenso, como si forzara la sonrisa."

# game/story.rpy:1359
translate spanish story_42fa1efe:

    # mc "Sounds like it, if she's half as awesome as you are."
    mc "Eso parece, si es que es la mitad de genial que tú."

# game/story.rpy:1360
translate spanish story_3c07690e:

    # cm "{i}I don't like the way she said that.{/i}"
    cm "{i}No me ha gustado nada cómo ha dicho eso.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1361
translate spanish story_7584f323:

    # mc "{b}Me neither{/b}."
    mc "{i}A mí tampoco{/i}."

# game/story.rpy:1362
translate spanish story_92cee879:

    # mc "Where do you guys meet up?"
    mc "¿Dónde os reunís?"

# game/story.rpy:1364
translate spanish story_c8d53617:

    # s "It's in a classroom for third year junior high schoolers."
    s "En un aula para alumnos de tercer año de secundaria."

# game/story.rpy:1366
translate spanish story_60dfb9ee:

    # "Third year junior high...that comes out to...ninth grade if I remember Japanese schooling right."
    "Tercer año de secundaria... Eso equivale a... noveno grado si recuerdo bien el sistema educativo japonés."

# game/story.rpy:1367
translate spanish story_64841097:

    # mc "Whoa, an entire classroom? Isn't that a bit big for only four people?"
    mc "Hala, ¿un aula entera? ¿No es un poco grande para solo cuatro personas?"

# game/story.rpy:1369
translate spanish story_df218174:

    # s "That was where the old Literature Club met, and when Monika went to apply to restart the club, she was told there were no normal clubrooms available anymore."
    s "Ahí es donde se reunía el antiguo club de literatura. Cuando Monika solicitó retomarlo, le dijeron que ya no quedaban salas de club normales."

# game/story.rpy:1371
translate spanish story_5fd132fa:

    # mc "Well, a nice big space only means there's more room to grow."
    mc "Bueno, tener tanto espacio significa que hay hueco para crecer."

# game/story.rpy:1373
translate spanish story_34b61c7e_2:

    # s "Yep!"
    s "¡Sí!"

# game/story.rpy:1375
translate spanish story_bd462ded:

    # s "So, what about you? What have you been doing?"
    s "Y dime, ¿qué hay de ti? ¿Qué has estado haciendo?"

# game/story.rpy:1377
translate spanish story_376652b2:

    # "I feel a wave of guilt wash over me from Meiji."
    "Siento una oleada de culpa invadiéndome de parte de Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:1378
translate spanish story_53e7dc61:

    # mc "Nothing much, I'm afraid. School, anime, manga, games and sleeping in on the weekends, that kind of thing."
    mc "Me temo que no mucho. El insti, anime, manga, videojuegos y dormir hasta tarde los fines de semana... Ese tipo de cosas."

# game/story.rpy:1379
translate spanish story_809a1e36:

    # s 4hj "That's not good! You need to be more active."
    s 4hj "¡Eso no es bueno! Tienes que ser más activo."

# game/story.rpy:1381
translate spanish story_b909d898:

    # mc "I know, that's why I wanted to do something fun today. I just woke up and felt...different."
    mc "Lo sé, por eso quería hacer algo divertido hoy. Simplemente me desperté y me sentí... diferente."

# game/story.rpy:1382
translate spanish story_ae71f089:

    # cm "{i}Noooo waaaaay!{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Ni de coña!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1383
translate spanish story_65d3f942:

    # s 1hh "Different how?"
    s 1hh "¿Diferente en qué sentido?"

# game/story.rpy:1385
translate spanish story_6b29011f:

    # "I fake a thoughtful look, as if I was trying to compose my thoughts."
    "Finjo una mirada pensativa, como si estuviera intentando ordenar mis ideas."

# game/story.rpy:1386
translate spanish story_5fe037a6:

    # mc "For the longest time I felt like I was a puppet on strings, just following a set schedule."
    mc "Durante mucho tiempo me sentí como una marioneta atada a unos hilos, simplemente siguiendo una rutina establecida."

# game/story.rpy:1387
translate spanish story_4b5dee52:

    # mc "I'd get up, go to school, come home, do homework and watch anime or read manga, then go to sleep. It's gotten monotonous."
    mc "Me levantaba, iba al instituto, volvía a casa, hacía los deberes, veía anime o leía manga y luego me iba a dormir. Se había vuelto monótono."

# game/story.rpy:1388
translate spanish story_7ae3507b:

    # cm "{i}Speak for yourself! I enjoy it...kind of.{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Habla por ti! Yo lo disfruto... más o menos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1389
translate spanish story_84c61293:

    # mc "When I woke up this morning, I had a realization. I don't want to let my last year of high school be as dry and boring as the others."
    mc "Cuando me desperté esta mañana, me di cuenta de algo. No quiero que mi último año de instituto sea tan soso y aburrido como los demás."

# game/story.rpy:1390
translate spanish story_e7052b2b:

    # mc "I want to have fun with my friends and you're the only real friend I have."
    mc "Quiero divertirme con mis amigos, y tú eres la única amiga de verdad que tengo."

# game/story.rpy:1391
translate spanish story_a871ee47:

    # mc "Even if we've been drifting apart slowly."
    mc "Incluso si nos hemos ido distanciando poco a poco."

# game/story.rpy:1392
translate spanish story_21b4ec7e:

    # mc "I decided that, starting today, I wanted to reconnect with you and try and make other friends too."
    mc "He decidido que, a partir de hoy, quiero volver a conectar contigo e intentar hacer otros amigos también."

# game/story.rpy:1393
translate spanish story_c789b028:

    # s 4hr "I'm happy to hear that!"
    s 4hr "¡Me hace muy feliz oír eso!"

# game/story.rpy:1395
translate spanish story_3c8ca832:

    # mc "Good. Now finish up your bun. We're going to have a fun day today. And starting tomorrow, we're going to spend time together like we used to."
    mc "Me alegro. Ahora termínate el bollo. Hoy vamos a pasar un día muy divertido. Y a partir de mañana, pasaremos tiempo juntos como solíamos hacerlo."

# game/story.rpy:1396
translate spanish story_867ae7c8:

    # mc "After your club, of course."
    mc "Después de tu club, por supuesto."

# game/story.rpy:1397
translate spanish story_50a743e1:

    # cm "{i}I hope you know what you're doing.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Espero que sepas lo que haces.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1398
translate spanish story_894f26be:

    # mc "{b}Believe me, so do I. I need her to invite me to the club after all. I can't change too much yet.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Créeme, yo también. Además, necesito que me invite al club. Aún no puedo cambiar demasiadas cosas.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1399
translate spanish story_50f61a07:

    # s 1hl "You don't have to go to all that trouble..."
    s 1hl "No tienes que tomarte tantas molestias..."

# game/story.rpy:1401
translate spanish story_0ae352f2:

    # mc "Hey, I like spending time with you."
    mc "Oye, que me gusta pasar tiempo contigo."

# game/story.rpy:1402
translate spanish story_403d08e5:

    # "I begin cleaning up my side of the table."
    "Empiezo a limpiar mi lado de la mesa."

# game/story.rpy:1404
translate spanish story_6ef3900d:

    # mc "You still going to finish that bun?"
    mc "¿Te vas a comer ese bollo?"

# game/story.rpy:1405
translate spanish story_8dbbd43a:

    # s 1hm "Oh yeah!"
    s 1hm "¡Ah, sí!"

# game/story.rpy:1407
translate spanish story_6accbf70:

    # "Sayori picks up the last bun, but to my surprise she breaks it in half, handing me the bigger piece."
    "Sayori agarra el último bollo, pero para mi sorpresa lo parte por la mitad, dándome el trozo más grande."

# game/story.rpy:1408
translate spanish story_3b4dfd2b:

    # s 2hx "Here you are."
    s 2hx "Aquí tienes."

# game/story.rpy:1410
translate spanish story_433038e3:

    # mc "Huh? Are you sure?"
    mc "¿Eh? ¿Estás segura?"

# game/story.rpy:1411
translate spanish story_787ab99f:

    # "She nods and extends it towards me. I take a hold of it and take a big bite."
    "Ella asiente y me lo ofrece. Lo cojo y le doy un gran bocado."

# game/story.rpy:1412
translate spanish story_812dc4b7:

    # "The sweetness overwhelms me this time and I have to balance the sweetness with the coffee's bitterness."
    "El dulzor me abruma esta vez y tengo que equilibrarlo con el amargor del café."

# game/story.rpy:1413
translate spanish story_f51bf433:

    # "Finally the table is clear of all the food."
    "Finalmente, no queda nada de comida en la mesa."

# game/story.rpy:1414
translate spanish story_ec81a30e:

    # mc "That was delicious."
    mc "Ha estado delicioso."

# game/story.rpy:1415
translate spanish story_b4c484e6:

    # s 1hq "Yeah, it was."
    s 1hq "Sí que lo estaba."

# game/story.rpy:1416
translate spanish story_71b7352e:

    # s 1ha "So, what next?"
    s 1ha "Y ahora, ¿qué sigue?"

# game/story.rpy:1417
translate spanish story_17cf0a92:

    # "I look at Meiji's phone. The time is now a few minutes past eleven."
    "Miro el teléfono de Meiji. Son poco más de las once de la mañana."

# game/story.rpy:1418
translate spanish story_8f55288c:

    # mc "Why don't we go walk off all the calories we just ate? Then we can go to the arcade."
    mc "¿Por qué no damos un paseo para quemar las calorías? Luego podemos ir a los salones recreativos."

# game/story.rpy:1420
translate spanish story_cf95c6be:

    # s "Yay!"
    s "¡Venga!"

# game/story.rpy:1422
translate spanish story_8640bff1:

    # "She wipes her face."
    "Se limpia la cara."

# game/story.rpy:1423
translate spanish story_841f0e46:

    # mc "I'm gonna clean up and meet you outside."
    mc "Voy a recoger esto y te veo afuera."

# game/story.rpy:1424
translate spanish story_06abe415:

    # s 1hx "Alright."
    s 1hx "Vale."

# game/story.rpy:1427
translate spanish story_7145b1d9:

    # "Sayori stands and rushes to the exit."
    "Ella se levanta y sale corriendo hacia la salida."

# game/story.rpy:1429
translate spanish story_8da10889:

    # "I throw out the garbage, place the tray on top with the others and follow."
    "Tiro la basura, coloco la bandeja encima de las demás y la sigo."

# game/story.rpy:1435
translate spanish story_5c71fd33:

    # "Sayori's on her phone busily texting someone. The day is a bit warmer but with the cold of late autumn still hanging in the air."
    "Sayori está absorta enviándole mensajes a alguien con el móvil. Hace un poco más de calor, pero todavía se nota en el ambiente el frío de finales de otoño."

# game/story.rpy:1436
translate spanish story_aca2b6de:

    # mc "Who are you texting?"
    mc "¿A quién le escribes?"

# game/story.rpy:1437
translate spanish story_c614aaa2:

    # "She quickly hides her phone."
    "Rápidamente, esconde el teléfono."

# game/story.rpy:1439
translate spanish story_9ce0b8b8:

    # s "Se-cr-et."
    s "Se"
    s "cre"
    s "to."

# game/story.rpy:1441
translate spanish story_09953b6c:

    # mc "Hmph, fine with me."
    mc "Jum, por mí bien."

# game/story.rpy:1442
translate spanish story_c6419463:

    # "I pretend to be hurt. I can't be too sure, but I think she's texting someone from the Literature Club about me joining."
    "Finjo estar dolido. No puedo estar muy seguro, pero creo que le está escribiendo a alguien del club de literatura para decirle que voy a unirme."

# game/story.rpy:1444
translate spanish story_79bdaef6:

    # s "Eh? Meiji, I didn't mean..."
    s "¿Eh? Meiji, no era mi intención..."

# game/story.rpy:1445
translate spanish story_c1055f0f:

    # "She looks away."
    "Ella aparta la mirada."

# game/story.rpy:1446
translate spanish story_981e889e:

    # mc "Hey, I'm kidding. I'm not the kind of guy who'd pry on your secrets. So, shall we go to the park?"
    mc "Oye, que es broma. No soy el tipo de chico que husmearía en tus secretos. Pero bueno, ¿vamos al parque?"

# game/story.rpy:1448
translate spanish story_34b61c7e_3:

    # s "Yep!"
    s "¡Sí!"

# game/story.rpy:1452
translate spanish story_3a0e6e3d:

    # "She falls into step with me and silence falls. I feel my heartbeat increase once again."
    "Se pone a caminar a mi lado y se hace el silencio. Siento cómo los latidos de mi corazón vuelven a acelerarse."

# game/story.rpy:1459
translate spanish story_51f5ec65:

    # s "Wow...it hasn't changed at all..."
    s "Vaya... no ha cambiado nada..."

# game/story.rpy:1460
translate spanish story_e3bd765c:

    # cm "{i}It really hasn't.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Desde luego que no.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1461
translate spanish story_6ac41a20:

    # mc "Well, I will say the company changed. They've grown cuter."
    mc "Bueno, diré que la compañía sí ha cambiado. Ahora es mucho más mona."

# game/story.rpy:1463
translate spanish story_4b76cc47:

    # cm "{i}I'd never say that!{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Yo nunca diría algo así!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1464
translate spanish story_9219f919:

    # mc "{b}But you would love to, right?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Pero te encantaría hacerlo, ¿a que sí?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1465
translate spanish story_3b63cdc9:

    # cm "{i}But…it's embarrassing.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Pero qué vergüenza...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1466
translate spanish story_4d206f3b:

    # mc "{b}She likes it, though. Look.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Sin embargo, a ella le gusta. Mira.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1467
translate spanish story_a5ba7a90:

    # s 1hy "C-Cute...?"
    s 1hy "¿M-Mona...?"

# game/story.rpy:1468
translate spanish story_4dfbd0d6:

    # mc "Yeah, you're very cute. It's one of the things I like about you. That, and how silly you are. I miss it."
    mc "Sí, eres muy mona. Es una de las cosas que me gustan de ti. Eso, y lo bobalicona que eres a veces. Lo echaba de menos."

# game/story.rpy:1469
translate spanish story_58bab67f:

    # s 1hl "Ehehe, thanks."
    s 1hl "Je, je, je, gracias."

# game/story.rpy:1471
translate spanish story_06cf864a:

    # mc "{b}Jackpot! We just scored some points with Sayori!{/b}"
    mc "{i}¡Bingo! ¡Acabamos de ganar unos cuantos puntos con Sayori!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1472
translate spanish story_e087fd09:

    # cm "{i}But it's not me doing it...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Pero no soy yo el que lo hace...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1473
translate spanish story_664ba2b1:

    # mc "{b}Don't worry, we'll tell everyone. And I know you really want to tell Sayori all of this, so it is you telling her in a sense.{/b}"
    mc "{i}No te preocupes, se lo contaremos a todas. Y sé que en el fondo te mueres por decirle todo esto a Sayori, así que en cierto modo, eres tú quien se lo está diciendo.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1474
translate spanish story_aaf1171b:

    # mc "{b}Sayori isn't the girl I'm after, anyway.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Que por cierto, Sayori no es la chica que me interesa.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1475
translate spanish story_c75b30be:

    # cm "{i}Really? Who are you after?{/i}"
    cm "{i}¿En serio? ¿Y a quién intentas conquistar?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1476
translate spanish story_74495499:

    # mc "{b}Se-cr-et.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Se{/i}"
    mc "{i}cre{/i}"
    mc "{i}to.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1477
translate spanish story_a3f68d55:

    # mc "{b}Don't worry about it. I drive, you navigate, amigo.{/b}"
    mc "{i}No te preocupes. Yo conduzco, tú me guías, amigo.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1478
translate spanish story_db416cab:

    # cm "{i}Yeah, yeah...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Sí, sí...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1480
translate spanish story_af195bac:

    # mc "So, Sayori, you've barely scratched the surface. How's your family been lately?"
    mc "Así que, Sayori, apenas hemos visto la punta del iceberg. ¿Cómo ha estado tu familia?"

# game/story.rpy:1481
translate spanish story_0d73a8a3:

    # s 2hx "They're doing great too. Dad's off on a business trip right now and he won't be back until after the Festival."
    s 2hx "Pues les va genial. Papá se ha ido a un viaje de negocios y no volverá hasta después del festival."

# game/story.rpy:1483
translate spanish story_8970659c:

    # s "Oh! And Mom's pregnant!"
    s "¡Ah! ¡Y mamá está embarazada!"

# game/story.rpy:1485
translate spanish story_ead2f488:

    # "My jaw drops, and I'm pretty sure Meiji's does too."
    "Me quedo con boquiabierto, y estoy bastante seguro de que a Meiji le pasa lo mismo."

# game/story.rpy:1486
translate spanish story_404476fc:

    # cm "{i}Holy...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Madre mía...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1487
translate spanish story_43c52d55:

    # mc "Sayori, that's fantastic!"
    mc "Sayori, ¡eso es fantástico!"

# game/story.rpy:1488
translate spanish story_a8b30f41:

    # "I see others looking at us with confused expressions nearby. Feeling embarrassed, I lower my voice."
    "Veo a otras personas cerca mirándonos con expresiones de confusión. Sintiéndome avergonzado, bajo la voz."

# game/story.rpy:1489
translate spanish story_25a2809c:

    # mc "You're gonna have a new little brother or sister, that's amazing."
    mc "Vas a tener un nuevo hermanito o hermanita, es increíble."

# game/story.rpy:1490
translate spanish story_d8df7065:

    # s 1hx "I'm happy too."
    s 1hx "Yo también estoy feliz."

# game/story.rpy:1492
translate spanish story_81232c19:

    # mc "Do you know when the baby's going to show up?"
    mc "¿Sabes cuándo nacerá el bebé?"

# game/story.rpy:1493
translate spanish story_d01e24cf:

    # s 1ho "I can't remember."
    s 1ho "No me acuerdo."

# game/story.rpy:1494
translate spanish story_8d5994d7:

    # s 2hc "April, I think."
    s 2hc "En abril, creo."

# game/story.rpy:1496
translate spanish story_494508c5:

    # mc "Good!"
    mc "¡Qué bien!"

# game/story.rpy:1497
translate spanish story_753c131e:

    # cm "{i}This is huge news. I hope we survive this…I want to see the little guy or girl.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Esto es una gran noticia. Espero que sobrevivamos a esto... Quiero ver al pequeño o a la pequeña.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1498
translate spanish story_5bc3eb76:

    # mc "{b}We will, bro.{/b}"
    mc "{b}Lo haremos, hermano.{/b}"

# game/story.rpy:1499
translate spanish story_8ebb34cb:

    # mc "Well how about school? Keeping up with your studies?"
    mc "Bueno, ¿y qué tal en el insti? ¿Llevas los estudios al día?"

# game/story.rpy:1500
translate spanish story_98b29ab3:

    # s 1hl "It's going alright..."
    s 1hl "Van bien..."

# game/story.rpy:1501
translate spanish story_6b266fb1:

    # s 2hj "...but I should be asking you that question."
    s 2hj "Pero yo debería ser la que te hiciera esa pregunta."

# game/story.rpy:1503
translate spanish story_41d2f570:

    # mc "{b}Heh, you're busted.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Je, te han pillado.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1504
translate spanish story_dfcbda87:

    # cm "{i}Oh, shut up!{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Calla!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1505
translate spanish story_33f521d6:

    # "I raise my hands in surrender."
    "Levanto las manos rindiéndome."

# game/story.rpy:1506
translate spanish story_c385a775:

    # mc "Heh, you caught me."
    mc "Venga, me has pillado."

# game/story.rpy:1507
translate spanish story_46df6174:

    # s 4hj "Honestly, I've been worried about you. You spend so much time inside with your manga and games."
    s 4hj "Siendo honesta, he estado preocupada por ti. Pasas demasiado tiempo encerrado con tu manga y tus videojuegos."

# game/story.rpy:1508
translate spanish story_6cb23363:

    # s 1hx "But...I am glad that you're deciding to try harder."
    s 1hx "Pero... me alegra que hayas decidido esforzarte más."

# game/story.rpy:1510
translate spanish story_e399e4ca:

    # mc "Ahaha, thanks. I'll try."
    mc "Ja, ja, ja, gracias. Lo intentaré."

# game/story.rpy:1511
translate spanish story_77a69a36:

    # s 1hx "Ehehe, I was surprised when you invited me out. You haven't in a while."
    s 1hx "Je, je, je. Me sorprendió que me invitaras a salir. Hace tiempo que no lo hacías."

# game/story.rpy:1513
translate spanish story_f23486ed:

    # mc "Yeah, well, I would like to do this more in the future."
    mc "Ya, bueno, me gustaría hacerlo más a menudo."

# game/story.rpy:1514
translate spanish story_b9073f97:

    # s 4hr "Yay!"
    s 4hr "¡Bieeen!"

# game/story.rpy:1520
translate spanish story_8d536be4:

    # "As we walk, a thought comes to mind."
    "Mientras caminamos, me viene un pensamiento a la mente."

# game/story.rpy:1521
translate spanish story_b0a4f66f:

    # mc "{b}Alright, you know her better than I do in certain areas, right? Why don't you ask something you want to know?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Vale, la conoces mejor que yo en algunos aspectos, ¿verdad? ¿Por qué no le preguntas algo que quieras saber?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1522
translate spanish story_307b2ead:

    # cm "{i}Ah, I, um…ask her if she still...oh what did she do again? Oh yeah! She collected seashells when we were kids.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Ah, yo, ehhh... pregúntale si todavía... ah, ¿qué era lo que hacía? ¡Ah, sí! Coleccionaba conchas marinas cuando éramos niños.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1523
translate spanish story_06e8f0eb:

    # mc "{b}Seashells eh? Really? Alright.{/b}"
    mc "{i}¿Conchas marinas, eh? ¿De verdad? Vale{/I}"

# game/story.rpy:1525
translate spanish story_7605e622:

    # mc "Hey, on another note, you collected seashells, right?"
    mc "Oye, cambiando de tema, tú coleccionabas conchas marinas, ¿verdad?"

# game/story.rpy:1526
translate spanish story_d1efbe6f:

    # s 2hc "Yeah, I did."
    s 2hc "Sí, así es."

# game/story.rpy:1528
translate spanish story_94f732e6:

    # "Whoa...Sayori collecting seashells? That's not something mentioned in the game or wiki."
    "Vaya... ¿Sayori coleccionando conchas marinas? Eso no se menciona en el juego ni en la wiki."

# game/story.rpy:1529
translate spanish story_8a8f85de:

    # "Although I suppose I can see her doing that."
    "Aunque supongo que me la puedo imaginar haciéndolo."

# game/story.rpy:1530
translate spanish story_1e9001bf:

    # mc "Are you still doing that?"
    mc "¿Aún lo haces?"

# game/story.rpy:1531
translate spanish story_be453dec:

    # s 1hl "Mmm...not as much. Since I helped start the Literature Club I haven't had as much time."
    s 1hl "Mmm... pues no tanto. Desde que ayudé a fundar el club de literatura, no tengo tanto tiempo."

# game/story.rpy:1532
translate spanish story_92fdac0b:

    # s "I haven't been as active lately."
    s "Últimamente no he sido muy activa."

# game/story.rpy:1534
translate spanish story_0cedf8ad:

    # "She pinches her stomach."
    "Se pellizca la barriga."

# game/story.rpy:1535
translate spanish story_8d940e23:

    # s 1hl "I've gotten a bit...um...flabby-"
    s 1hl "Me he puesto un poco... mmm... fofa..."

# game/story.rpy:1537
translate spanish story_6b7e7683:

    # s "-Ehehehehe!!!!"
    s "¡Je, je, je!"

# game/story.rpy:1539
translate spanish story_5030b142:

    # "I move forward and begin tickling her stomach."
    "Me acerco y empiezo a hacerle cosquillas en la barriga."

# game/story.rpy:1540
translate spanish story_3ab8b310:

    # s 4hzi "Not theeeeere! I'm tickliiiish!"
    s 4hzi "¡Ahííí no, que tengo cosquillasss!"

# game/story.rpy:1542
translate spanish story_d30017ef:

    # "She squirms and I laugh. I can hear Meiji laughing as well."
    "Se retuerce y me río. También puedo oír a Meiji riéndose."

# game/story.rpy:1543
translate spanish story_4dc0773d:

    # mc "Well you don't feel flabeeeheehee, or flabby for that matter. You're fine. I'm sure you've put just as much work into your club as you do collecting seashells."
    mc "Pues no se te nota taaan fofa, ni nada por el estilo. Estás bien. Seguro que le pones tanto esfuerzo a tu club como lo hacías coleccionando conchas."

# game/story.rpy:1549
translate spanish story_b734fefa:

    # "We've walked around the park almost once by this point."
    "Sin darme cuenta, ya hemos dado casi una vuelta completa al parque."

# game/story.rpy:1550
translate spanish story_f7f0cdf6:

    # "I see that we're coming towards a part of the park made for kids."
    "Veo que nos acercamos a una zona diseñada para niños."

# game/story.rpy:1552
translate spanish story_463d97ea:

    # "I then hear Sayori's stomach growling."
    "Entonces escucho rugir el estómago de Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:1553
translate spanish story_1012f60f:

    # s 1hy "Ehehe, sorry Meiji. Guess those buns weren't enough."
    s 1hy "Je, je, je, lo siento. Creo que esos bollos no fueron suficientes."

# game/story.rpy:1554
translate spanish story_a26ef216:

    # mc "No kidding. Let's see..."
    mc "Ya te digo. A ver..."

# game/story.rpy:1559
translate spanish story_02513e4d:

    # "I look around."
    "Miro a mi alrededor."

# game/story.rpy:1560
translate spanish story_be94f4e2:

    # "We're passing some public park bathrooms with a few vending machines nearby as well."
    "Pasamos por unos baños públicos, con unas cuantas máquinas expendedoras cerca."

# game/story.rpy:1562
translate spanish story_ffff3f52:

    # mc "Alright, why don't we stop and get a snack? It's still a bit early for lunch."
    mc "Vale, ¿por qué no paramos y cogemos algo de picar? Todavía es un poco pronto para comer."

# game/story.rpy:1564
translate spanish story_cf95c6be_1:

    # s "Yay!"
    s "¡Venga, vamos!"

# game/story.rpy:1567
translate spanish story_9ba7d662:

    # "We head over to the vending machines."
    "Nos dirigimos a las máquinas expendedoras."

# game/story.rpy:1568
translate spanish story_e42fb487:

    # "As Sayori is busy drooling over the various choices, I look more closely at the world around me."
    "Mientras Sayori babea frente a las diversas opciones, observo con más atención el mundo que me rodea."

# game/story.rpy:1569
translate spanish story_b665949c:

    # "It certainly looks real."
    "Desde luego, parece real."

# game/story.rpy:1570
translate spanish story_c279ff5c:

    # "The brands I see look similar to the ones I'm familiar with, but the names are weird."
    "Las marcas que veo se parecen a las que conozco, pero los nombres son extraños."

# game/story.rpy:1571
translate spanish story_0088af89:

    # "Fansa...? Yamune...? Why are the brand names off by a letter or two?"
    "¿Fansa...? ¿Yamune...? ¿Por qué los nombres de las marcas cambian por una o dos letras?"

# game/story.rpy:1572
translate spanish story_9787743c:

    # "Well, that's not as important now."
    "Bueno, eso no es tan importante ahora."

# game/story.rpy:1577
translate spanish story_7cbeb499:

    # "I kneel and pick up some dirt and rub it in my hands."
    "Me arrodillo, recojo un poco de tierra y me la froto en las manos."

# game/story.rpy:1578
translate spanish story_2efe128c:

    # "The dirt is incredibly real and I feel it between my fingertips, watching the excess fall to the ground gently."
    "La tierra es increíblemente real, la siento entre las yemas de los dedos, viendo cómo el exceso cae suavemente al suelo."

# game/story.rpy:1579
translate spanish story_b1c575d4:

    # "I gently pinch myself and feel the slight pain. Everything around me is so realistic."
    "Me pellizco suavemente y siento el ligero dolor. Todo a mi alrededor es tan realista."

# game/story.rpy:1580
translate spanish story_2660fc27:

    # "There are a couple children playing on the playground."
    "Hay un par de niños jugando en la zona infantil."

# game/story.rpy:1586
translate spanish story_8a64e225:

    # "Looking back, I see Sayori standing in front of a vending machine. I can see her salivating as I walk up."
    "Miro hacia atrás y veo a Sayori de pie frente a una máquina expendedora. Puedo ver cómo babea a medida que me acerco."

# game/story.rpy:1587
translate spanish story_bba10a95:

    # s 4hx "Meiji, look look! This is new!"
    s 4hx "¡Meiji, mira, mira! ¡Esto es nuevo!"

# game/story.rpy:1589
translate spanish story_f2efe329:

    # "She points to the vending machine. I look at it and see that it's a type that can provide a small pizza in minutes."
    "Señala la máquina. La miro y me doy cuenta de que es de las que preparan una pizza pequeña en cuestión de minutos."

# game/story.rpy:1590
translate spanish story_af88938f:

    # mc "Ahaha, calm down. I'll get it for you."
    mc "Ja, ja, ja. Cálmate. Te compraré una."

# game/story.rpy:1592
translate spanish story_91ffef1b:

    # "Before she can protest, I slip a thousand yen bill inside and press the button. An automated voice tells me it will be a few minutes before the pizza is ready."
    "Antes de que pueda rechistar, meto un billete de mil yenes en la ranura y pulso el botón. Una voz automatizada me informa de que la pizza tardará un par de minutos."

# game/story.rpy:1594
translate spanish story_3b540074:

    # "I grab my change and then buy a soda, a small sandwich and some chips from another couple of machines."
    "Cojo el cambio y compro un refresco, un sándwich pequeño y unas patatas fritas en un par de máquinas más."

# game/story.rpy:1600
translate spanish story_d5f045d5:

    # "I sit down on a bench with Sayori, who would steal glances at my food."
    "Me siento en un banco con Sayori, que no le quita ojo a mi comida."

# game/story.rpy:1601
translate spanish story_7d11d46d:

    # "Sighing as if acquiescing to her, I turn the bag of chips her way."
    "Suspiro, dándome por vencido, y le ofrezco la bolsa de patatas."

# game/story.rpy:1603
translate spanish story_1c699d7a:

    # "She gleefully begins eating."
    "Empieza a comérselas contentísima."

# game/story.rpy:1604
translate spanish story_b896c9f6:

    # mc "{b}Meiji, any other questions we can ask her?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Meiji, ¿podemos hacerle alguna otra pregunta?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1605
translate spanish story_98d99fee:

    # cm "{i}Eh? Oh! Um, sorry, I was reminiscing.{/i}"
    cm "{i}¿Eh? ¡Ah! Sí, perdona. Estaba recordando viejos tiempos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1606
translate spanish story_f1f2d27f:

    # mc "{b}What about?{/b}"
    mc "{i}¿Cómo qué?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1612
translate spanish story_a1b74dbd:

    # "Meiji shows me a memory."
    "Meiji me muestra un recuerdo."

# game/story.rpy:1613
translate spanish story_4727c98c:

    # "I see Meiji and a childhood Sayori run around while four adults sit and talk."
    "Veo a Meiji y a Sayori de pequeños corriendo de un lado para otro mientras cuatro adultos están sentados charlando."

# game/story.rpy:1614
translate spanish story_ede45eba:

    # "I recognize two of whom I recognize as Meiji's parents. I see Sayori's mom as well."
    "Reconozco a los padres de Meiji. También está la madre de Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:1615
translate spanish story_fd792526:

    # "I almost flinch as Sayori stumbles and skins her knee while trying to climb up to go down the red slide."
    "Casi me estremezco cuando Sayori tropieza y se raspa la rodilla al intentar trepar por el tobogán rojo."

# game/story.rpy:1616
translate spanish story_28d2e5f8:

    # "She begins to cry and I watch as Meiji rushes to her side. I'm so busy looking at the past through Meiji's eyes that I don't hear Sayori calling out to me."
    "Se echa a llorar y veo cómo Meiji corre a socorrerla. Estoy tan absorto mirando el pasado a través de los ojos de Meiji que no escucho a Sayori llamarme."

# game/story.rpy:1623
translate spanish story_2e563eea:

    # s "Meiji? You okay?"
    s "¿Meiji? ¿Estás bien?"

# game/story.rpy:1624
translate spanish story_0e33b5fd:

    # mc "Huh? What?"
    mc "¿Eh? ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/story.rpy:1626
translate spanish story_718010d2:

    # s 2hh "You okay? You were spacing out."
    s 2hh "¿Estás bien? Te habías quedado empanado."

# game/story.rpy:1628
translate spanish story_0a5b9d08:

    # mc "Ah sorry. I was just thinking back to when we were kids and we came here."
    mc "Ah, perdona. Estaba recordando cuando veníamos aquí de pequeños."

# game/story.rpy:1629
translate spanish story_48c9b1e1:

    # "I notice that Sayori has her pizza already."
    "Me doy cuenta de que Sayori ya tiene su pizza."

# game/story.rpy:1630
translate spanish story_bf51e308:

    # "I point over to the spot I saw in Meiji's memory."
    "Señalo hacia el lugar que vi en el recuerdo de Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:1631
translate spanish story_6f77915b:

    # mc "Hey, there's that slide where you fell back when you and I were kids."
    mc "Mira, ahí está el tobogán donde te caíste cuando éramos unos críos."

# game/story.rpy:1632
translate spanish story_a03ab648:

    # s 1hy "I remember that... This place wasn't so crowded back then."
    s 1hy "Me acuerdo de eso... Este sitio no estaba tan lleno en aquel entonces."

# game/story.rpy:1633
translate spanish story_b9c73b19:

    # mc "You sound like an older adult when you say that."
    mc "Hablas como una persona mayor."

# game/story.rpy:1634
translate spanish story_c07681fc:

    # cm "{i}Good one!{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Esa estuvo buena!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1635
translate spanish story_5b228297:

    # s 1hzp "Meanie..."
    s 1hzp "Malo..."

# game/story.rpy:1636
translate spanish story_1b891a3b:

    # mc "Oho? A meanie, am I?"
    mc "¿Ah, sí? ¿Conque soy malo?"

# game/story.rpy:1637
translate spanish story_c3535549:

    # "I hold up both my hands and make tickling motions."
    "Levanto las manos y hago el gesto de hacer cosquillas."

# game/story.rpy:1638
translate spanish story_59aedc27:

    # mc "Uahahaha!"
    mc "¡Muajajaja!"

# game/story.rpy:1639
translate spanish story_7f71ffba:

    # s 4hzi "Aaaah! Not the tickle monster again!"
    s 4hzi "¡Ahhh! ¡El monstruo de las cosquillas no!"

# game/story.rpy:1641
translate spanish story_46b7ecb6:

    # "A few seconds later we both start laughing."
    "Unos segundos después, los dos nos echamos a reír."

# game/story.rpy:1642
translate spanish story_5463e8e9:

    # s 1hl "Ahaha, thanks, Meiji. I needed that laugh..."
    s 1hl "Ja, ja, ja. Gracias, Meiji. Me hacía falta reírme un rato..."

# game/story.rpy:1644
translate spanish story_03df7d67:

    # cm "{i}Even I could have guessed something was wrong just from that sentence...I think{/i}."
    cm "{i}Hasta yo me habría dado cuenta de que algo va mal solo con esa frase..., creo.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1645
translate spanish story_2f38578b:

    # mc "I like seeing you laugh. Makes me feel happy knowing I could help make you happy in even the smallest ways."
    mc "Me gusta verte reír. Me hace feliz saber que puedo ayudarte a estar contenta, aunque sea con una tontería."

# game/story.rpy:1646
translate spanish story_5018927f:

    # s 1hl "You're too kind to me, Meiji..."
    s 1hl "Eres demasiado bueno conmigo, Meiji..."

# game/story.rpy:1647
translate spanish story_e5cf06a3:

    # mc "I learned from the master."
    mc "He aprendido de la maestra."

# game/story.rpy:1649
translate spanish story_64d494aa:

    # "I give an exaggerated bow. and we both laugh."
    "Hago una reverencia exagerada y los dos nos reímos."

# game/story.rpy:1651
translate spanish story_c2c46844:

    # "But my face falls a little bit later."
    "Pero mi sonrisa se desvanece un poco después."

# game/story.rpy:1653
translate spanish story_5a4bb4a6:

    # mc "Seriously, Sayori, you're the one who's been too good to me. More than I deserve."
    mc "En serio, Sayori, tú eres la que se ha portado demasiado bien conmigo. Más de lo que merezco."

# game/story.rpy:1655
translate spanish story_56c502ca:

    # "I can practically feel the guilt pouring off of Meiji."
    "Casi puedo sentir cómo la culpa emana de Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:1656
translate spanish story_9889bca0:

    # mc "{b}It's alright, if anything else I forgive you. What I'm about to say is not a slight to you in any way. I know you're a good person.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Tranquilo. Si te sirve de algo, te perdono. Lo que voy a decir no es un ataque hacia ti. Sé que eres una buena persona.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1657
translate spanish story_e56a332d:

    # s 4hf "Meiji? Are you alright?"
    s 4hf "¿Meiji? ¿Estás bien?"

# game/story.rpy:1658
translate spanish story_ab39984f:

    # "I smile sadly and shake my head."
    "Esbozo una sonrisa triste y niego con la cabeza."

# game/story.rpy:1659
translate spanish story_e5f344ab:

    # mc "Not as much as I'd like. I haven't exactly been the best friend, have I?"
    mc "No tan bien como me gustaría. No he sido precisamente el mejor de los amigos, ¿verdad?"

# game/story.rpy:1661
translate spanish story_49c95ed0:

    # s "What do you mean?"
    s "¿A qué te refieres?"

# game/story.rpy:1662
translate spanish story_22538e47:

    # "I take a deep breath to calm Meiji and myself down. I turn to her again, the sad smile still on my face."
    "Respiro hondo para calmarnos tanto a Meiji como a mí mismo. Me vuelvo hacia ella sin perder esa sonrisa amarga."

# game/story.rpy:1663
translate spanish story_f66e8d16:

    # mc "Sayori, when was the last time we ever did anything like this? Just you and me, best friends, hanging out together?"
    mc "Sayori, ¿cuándo fue la última vez que hicimos algo así? Solo tú y yo, dos mejores amigos, pasando el rato juntos."

# game/story.rpy:1665
translate spanish story_7719dc86:

    # "Sayori comes over and sits next to me. I feel a comforting hand on my back as she runs it up and down."
    "Sayori se acerca y se sienta a mi lado. Siento su mano reconfortante recorriéndome la espalda de arriba a abajo."

# game/story.rpy:1666
translate spanish story_107972d3:

    # "In that moment, I see someone mature and caring trying to cheer up someone she cares about."
    "En ese momento, veo a una persona madura y atenta que intenta animar a alguien que le importa."

# game/story.rpy:1667
translate spanish story_f45bbd38:

    # "Any hint of her normal childish behavior is gone, replaced with a mature and caring attitude which reminds me a bit of her mother."
    "Cualquier rastro de su habitual comportamiento infantil ha desaparecido y ha sido reemplazado por una actitud madura y protectora que me recuerda un poco a su madre."

# game/story.rpy:1668
translate spanish story_c251d7e6:

    # s "Meiji...don't look so down. You didn't do anything wrong."
    s "Meiji, no te desanimes. No has hecho nada malo."

# game/story.rpy:1669
translate spanish story_2e4ea1d5:

    # mc "But I did."
    mc "Sí que lo he hecho."

# game/story.rpy:1670
translate spanish story_0ad96f13:

    # "I utilize Meiji's guilt mixed with mine at lying to her. I need to sound convincing."
    "Aprovecho la culpa de Meiji y la mezclo con la mía por estar mintiéndole. Tengo que sonar convincente."

# game/story.rpy:1671
translate spanish story_9beda61c:

    # "I smile sadly at her."
    "Le dedico otra sonrisa triste."

# game/story.rpy:1672
translate spanish story_0db1e9f2:

    # mc "Friendship is a two-way street, and you've put more work into walking that street than I have."
    mc "La amistad es algo de dos y tú te has esforzado muchísimo más que yo en mantenerla."

# game/story.rpy:1673
translate spanish story_906db0e7:

    # mc "I woke up early this morning and realized what a jerk I've been to you..."
    mc "Esta mañana me he despertado temprano y me he dado cuenta de lo capullo que he sido contigo..."

# game/story.rpy:1674
translate spanish story_1fed2aab:

    # cm "{i}Certainly feels like you're blaming me...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Pues sí que parece que me estás echando la culpa...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1675
translate spanish story_8800dfec:

    # mc "{b}Look dude, we all make mistakes. Do you want to make this up to her?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Mira, tío, todos cometemos errores. ¿Quieres compensarla o no?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1676
translate spanish story_abc18955:

    # cm "{i}...Yes...more than anything...she's my best friend and the girl I'm in love with...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Sí... Más que nada en el mundo... Es mi mejor amiga y la chica de la que estoy enamorado...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1677
translate spanish story_0ceac09a:

    # mc "{b}Let me handle it until we find a way to let you take control.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Déjamelo a mí hasta que encontremos la forma de que vuelvas a tomar el control.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1678
translate spanish story_b6a29605:

    # cm "{i}Alright...I hope I'm right in trusting you...{/i}"
    cm "{i}Vale. Espero no equivocarme al confiar en ti...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1679
translate spanish story_ed53140f:

    # "Me too..."
    "Eso espero..."

# game/story.rpy:1680
translate spanish story_c91f21d1:

    # s "Meiji...I forgive you."
    s "Meiji... Te perdono."

# game/story.rpy:1682
translate spanish story_4d695dbb:

    # "The maturity in the voice of someone normally hyper and childlike is a welcome surprise."
    "La madurez en la voz de alguien que normalmente es tan hiperactiva e infantil es una sorpresa muy agradable."

# game/story.rpy:1683
translate spanish story_a30d74be:

    # "What's even more of a surprise is the sudden tender hug that Sayori suddenly gives me."
    "Pero lo que más me sorprende es el tierno y repentino abrazo que me da Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:1684
translate spanish story_36e62f78:

    # "I respond by hugging back. Her hugs are so warm and comforting. I feel myself relax a bit."
    "Le devuelvo el abrazo. Sus abrazos son tan cálidos y reconfortantes... Siento cómo me relajo un poco."

# game/story.rpy:1685
translate spanish story_3bbb6a7d:

    # "She holds me close, running her hands up and down my back."
    "Me aprieta contra ella, acariciándome la espalda de arriba a abajo."

# game/story.rpy:1686
translate spanish story_3dfad4f1:

    # s 1hzzzf "Hey, everything's okay. I promise."
    s 1hzzzf "Oye, todo va a salir bien. Te lo prometo."

# game/story.rpy:1687
translate spanish story_347bc141:

    # "She strokes my hair softly. I chuckle a bit."
    "Me acaricia el pelo con suavidad. Se me escapa una pequeña risa."

# game/story.rpy:1688
translate spanish story_3ef3aa3e:

    # mc "I'm going to make it up to you, starting today. And tomorrow, I'll wait around to walk home with you after your club ends."
    mc "Voy a compensarte desde hoy mismo. Y mañana, te esperaré a que termines el club para volver juntos a casa."

# game/story.rpy:1693
translate spanish story_7c8fce19:

    # s "You mean it?! You'll wait for me?"
    s "¡¿Lo dices en serio?! ¿Me vas a esperar?"

# game/story.rpy:1696
translate spanish story_f4e481e2:

    # mc "Sure, I will. I miss walking home with you."
    mc "Claro que sí. Echo de menos volver a casa contigo."

# game/story.rpy:1698
translate spanish story_cf95c6be_2:

    # s "Yay!"
    s "¡Bieeen!"

# game/story.rpy:1700
translate spanish story_6d2d164a:

    # "She finishes up her pizza and rubs her belly satisfied."
    "Se termina su pizza y se frota la barriga, satisfecha."

# game/story.rpy:1701
translate spanish story_934709d6:

    # s 2hr "That was so good!"
    s 2hr "¡Estaba riquísima!"

# game/story.rpy:1703
translate spanish story_64e93c02:

    # mc "Good to know. I'll try it sometime. Come on, we should head to our next venue. The arcade!"
    mc "Es bueno saberlo. La probaré algún día. Venga, deberíamos ir a nuestro siguiente destino. ¡A los recreativos!"

# game/story.rpy:1706
translate spanish story_3cb17596:

    # "Sayori runs towards the park exit."
    "Sayori sale corriendo hacia la salida."

# game/story.rpy:1711
translate spanish story_1d39409f:

    # "I quickly throw the garbage away and run after her, but by this time she's nearly out of sight."
    "Tiro rápido la basura y corro tras ella, pero a estas alturas casi la he perdido de vista."

# game/story.rpy:1712
translate spanish story_034c4483:

    # mc "{b}She must really love the arcade.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Se nota a leguas que le encantan los recreativos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1713
translate spanish story_f6625181:

    # cm "{i}Oh yeah, she does.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Y que lo digas.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1714
translate spanish story_fe5972fd:

    # cm "{i}When we were younger our parents would give us about two thousand yen each and we'd go nuts there.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Cuando éramos pequeños, nuestros padres nos daban unos dos mil yenes a cada uno y nos volvíamos locos ahí dentro.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1715
translate spanish story_41f15a97:

    # cm "{i}She especially loved the racing games. She always kicked my ass at those though.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Le encantaban sobre todo los juegos de carreras. Aunque siempre me daba una paliza en esos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1716
translate spanish story_c62dd19d:

    # cm "{i}I wonder if our usernames are still listed in that racing game she and I used to play.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Me pregunto si nuestros usuarios seguirán en el juego de carreras al que jugábamos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1717
translate spanish story_7bf66ab5:

    # mc "{b}You've got those here too!? Oh, hell yes!{/b}"
    mc "{i}¡¿También tenéis de esos aquí?! ¡Ah, joder, claro que sí!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1718
translate spanish story_1d8b962f:

    # "I pump my legs harder, but it's obvious Meiji's body isn't as in shape as my own."
    "Aprieto el paso, pero es evidente que el cuerpo de Meiji no está tan en forma como el mío."

# game/story.rpy:1726
translate spanish story_5895c715:

    # "Soon we reach the arcade."
    "Poco después llegamos a los recreativos."

# game/story.rpy:1727
translate spanish story_1894f77d:

    # "Sayori's already sitting at the racing game, looking at me expectantly."
    "Sayori ya está sentada en el juego de carreras y me mira expectante."

# game/story.rpy:1728
translate spanish story_2a74f85d:

    # "I walk over to a change-making machine, put in a thousand yen and, after taking and counting the change to make sure I wasn't shorted, I turn."
    "Me acerco a una máquina de cambio, meto mil yenes y, tras coger y contar las monedas para asegurarme de que no falta nada, me doy la vuelta."

# game/story.rpy:1729
translate spanish story_915994d0:

    # "She's still waiting. I make a show of cracking my knuckles and neck, then walk over and sit."
    "Sigue esperando. Hago el teatro de crujirme los nudillos y el cuello antes de acercarme y sentarme."

# game/story.rpy:1730
translate spanish story_729eba8e:

    # mc "Let the rematch of all rematches begin."
    mc "Que comience la madre de todas las revanchas."

# game/story.rpy:1731
translate spanish story_1febc162:

    # s 3hzw "Prepare to lose again!"
    s 3hzw "¡Prepárate para perder otra vez!"

# game/story.rpy:1732
translate spanish story_9b4f18f1:

    # mc "{b}Whoa, this is a new side to her I never expected.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Hala, no me esperaba para nada esta faceta suya.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1733
translate spanish story_c6ae25c1:

    # cm "{i}She's weirdly competitive when it comes to arcade games.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Es extrañamente competitiva cuando se trata de juegos recreativos.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1734
translate spanish story_1b68ae78:

    # mc "{b}Fair enough.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Me mola.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1735
translate spanish story_ac6c9981:

    # "I log into Meiji's account. I see that Meiji has put all the upgrades in every car."
    "Inicio sesión en la cuenta de Meiji. Veo que le ha puesto todas las mejoras a todos los coches."

# game/story.rpy:1736
translate spanish story_c8132a7a:

    # mc "{b}Jesus Christ...how much money did you sink into this game?{/b}"
    mc "{i}Madre del amor hermoso... ¿Cuánto dinero te has dejado en este juego?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1737
translate spanish story_747bccb3:

    # cm "{i}More than I want to admit.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Más del que me gustaría admitir.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:1738
translate spanish story_f2dfd3eb:

    # s 1hzy "Ready?"
    s 1hzy "¿Listo?"

# game/story.rpy:1739
translate spanish story_d48fb61f:

    # mc "Oh, bring it on! I'm so gonna kick your ass!"
    mc "¡Ah, venga ya! ¡Te voy a dar una paliza!"

# game/story.rpy:1740
translate spanish story_1e766c6c:

    # s 4hzz "Let's go!"
    s 4hzz "¡Vamos allá!"

# game/story.rpy:1746
translate spanish story_057b0a65:

    # "In total, I probably sunk about five thousand yen of Meiji's money into the matches."
    "En total, puede que me haya fundido unos cinco mil yenes del dinero de Meiji en las partidas."

# game/story.rpy:1747
translate spanish story_ca0fc34f:

    # "I'd lose some, Sayori would lose others, but we were evenly matched. We playfully trash talked each other and generally had a good time."
    "Yo perdía algunas, Sayori perdía otras, pero estábamos muy igualados. Nos picábamos de broma y, en general, pasamos un buen rato."

# game/story.rpy:1748
translate spanish story_793042f4:

    # "It helped that I knew how to drive, though."
    "Claro que saber conducir también me ayudó bastante."

# game/story.rpy:1754
translate spanish story_7f83d5a3:

    # "A few hours later I look at my phone and realize it's later than expected."
    "Unas horas después miro el móvil y me doy cuenta de que es más tarde de lo que pensaba."

# game/story.rpy:1755
translate spanish story_403d46e8:

    # mc "Whoa, it's late. I need to get you home."
    mc "Hala, es muy tarde. Tengo que llevarte a casa."

# game/story.rpy:1757
translate spanish story_204c519a:

    # s "Awww, can't we stay? Please?"
    s "Jolín, ¿no podemos quedarnos? ¿Por fa?"

# game/story.rpy:1759
translate spanish story_b8c3e9ae:

    # "She gives me puppy dog eyes."
    "Me pone ojitos de cachorrito."

# game/story.rpy:1760
translate spanish story_f316193b:

    # mc "No. I'm tired and it looks like you are too. I don't want you oversleeping and being late to school."
    mc "Que va. Estoy cansado ya y tú también tienes pinta de estarlo. No quiero que te quedes dormida y llegues tarde a clase."

# game/story.rpy:1761
translate spanish story_4f1dd889:

    # s 1hy "Let me use the bathroom really fast."
    s 1hy "Déjame ir al baño un segundito."

# game/story.rpy:1764
translate spanish story_1938c14b:

    # "I use the bathroom as well and then we leave."
    "Yo también voy al baño, ya luego nos marchamos."

# game/story.rpy:1772
translate spanish story_f0922485:

    # "The sun is just beginning to set. The air is cooler and Sayori is shivering despite her own coat."
    "El sol está empezando a ponerse. El aire es más frío y Sayori está temblando a pesar de llevar su propio abrigo."

# game/story.rpy:1773
translate spanish story_cb8a2c71:

    # "I chuckle when I see that and hand her my own coat."
    "Me río un poco al verla y le tiendo el mío."

# game/story.rpy:1775
translate spanish story_1a62ae18:

    # "Wordlessly she takes it and wraps it around her. We walk in silence for a bit."
    "Lo coge sin decir ni una palabra y se envuelve en él. Caminamos en silencio un rato."

# game/story.rpy:1776
translate spanish story_65b4add4:

